## Provider

**Provider:** {{EMBEDDINGS_PROVIDER}}
**Model:** {{EMBEDDINGS_MODEL}}
**Dimensions:** {{EMBEDDINGS_DIMENSIONS}}

<!-- Provider options:
  - faiss      — Local FAISS index. No external dependencies. Best for single-machine setups.
  - chromadb   — Local or client-server ChromaDB. Good for development and small-to-medium corpora.
  - pgvector   — PostgreSQL extension. Best when you already have a Postgres database.
  - openai     — OpenAI embeddings API (text-embedding-3-small/large). Requires API key.
  - gemini     — Google Gemini embeddings API. Requires API key.
-->

### Provider-Specific Configuration

{{#PROVIDER_FAISS}}
```yaml
provider: faiss
index_path: "{{EMBEDDINGS_STORAGE_PATH}}/faiss.index"
metadata_path: "{{EMBEDDINGS_STORAGE_PATH}}/metadata.json"
# FAISS runs entirely local. No API keys needed.
# Index type: Flat (exact) for < 100k vectors, IVF for larger corpora.
```
{{/PROVIDER_FAISS}}

{{#PROVIDER_CHROMADB}}
```yaml
provider: chromadb
persist_directory: "{{EMBEDDINGS_STORAGE_PATH}}/chroma/"
# For client-server mode:
# host: "localhost"
# port: 8000
```
{{/PROVIDER_CHROMADB}}

{{#PROVIDER_PGVECTOR}}
```yaml
provider: pgvector
connection_string: "${DATABASE_URL}"
# Requires: CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS vector;
# Table is auto-created per collection.
```
{{/PROVIDER_PGVECTOR}}

{{#PROVIDER_OPENAI}}
```yaml
provider: openai
api_key: "${OPENAI_API_KEY}"
model: "text-embedding-3-small"  # or text-embedding-3-large
# Cost: ~$0.02 per 1M tokens (small), ~$0.13 per 1M tokens (large)
```
{{/PROVIDER_OPENAI}}

{{#PROVIDER_GEMINI}}
```yaml
provider: gemini
api_key: "${GEMINI_API_KEY}"
model: "text-embedding-004"
```
{{/PROVIDER_GEMINI}}

